cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.CV 

The paper discusses training logistic regression and SVM on a large dataset using minwise hashing, which is a common technique in machine learning and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of GPUs, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and data storage (cs.DB). Finally, the paper deals with large-scale data processing, which is a topic in distributed systems (cs.DS).
